        <mxCell id="2" value="单 Agent 优化实际主链路总览&#xa;代码落地状态对照：Web -&gt; Gateway -&gt; Core Runtime -&gt; Tool/Skill/MCP/Jar -&gt; SSE/Trace/Memory" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=20;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacingLeft=18;" vertex="1" parent="1">
